==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: New Years Day
<hw>New" Year's` Day"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>the first day of a
calendar year; the first day of January. Often colloquially abbreviated
to <altname>New year's</altname> or <altname>new
year</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>New Zealand</ent>⟦br⟧
